text: Cheiry (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 104) was a municipality in Broye in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. Since 2005, Chapelle became a part of Cheiry. On 1 January 2021, Cheiry became a part of Surpierre. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
